'''Jedi!''' was a critically acclaimed play, written and performed by [[Actor/Legends|actor]] [[Palleus Chuff]]. The story featured [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] (as portrayed by Chuff). In act three scene two, Yoda set his [[Starship/Legends|ship's]] [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] to [[Self-destruct mechanism/Legends|self-destruct]] before fleeing in an [[Escape pod/Legends|escape pod]] to elude pursuing [[Tholian]]s. It was very popular and could be watched during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. By the time of the [[Mission to Vjun (Clone Wars)|Mission to Vjun]], Chuff had performed Jedi! 1,437 times. [[TriNebulon News/Legends|TriNebulon News]] described Jedi! as "an astonishing re-creation of the Grand Master himself" and gave Chuff's performance four stars.

